  <prompt>
    Author `WriteSessionMemoryHandler` (NEW) at `src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Handlers/WriteSessionMemoryHandler.cs` implementing the T2 `write_session_memory({fact, source, confidence, category?})` tool per architecture ¬ß8.1. Writes a structured fact to the current session's T2 memory (NOT T3 ‚Äî promotion is explicit via task 088). Returns `{ factId }`. The fact lives only in the active session (24h Redis hot / 90d Cosmos warm per ¬ß3.1). Implements FR-30 (write_session_memory row of the 8-tool surface).
